description:
KnowledgeWoods PMP® Exam Prep is a power-packed, Udemy Featured course designed to help PMP® Aspirants Pass the exam at the Very First Attempt.

    This PMP Exam Prep Course is up to date with the framework of knowledge outlined by the Project Management Institute's Guide to Project Management Body of Knowledge – PMBoK® Fifth Edition and latest PMP® Examination Blue Print.

      Salient Features:-

      • PMP® Certification Exam Overview Module comprising of Exam Pattern, Question Types, How to Pass PMP® Exam at First Attempt
      • Downloadable Project Management Templates, ITTO Sheets & Process MindMaps
      • Real World Scenarios to introduce Key Project Management Concepts
      • PMP® Exam Essentials & Module End Questions for each Knowledge Area
      • 5 PMP® Mock Exams at KnowledgeWoods' Platform
      • PMP® Mathematics Module - all Formulae based questions with example
      • 35 PDUs/Contact Hours Certificate by PMI Global REP
      • Assistance in PMP® Certification Application Filing
      • Job Aids for Better Understanding of Project Deliverables


      Please feel free to get in touch with us for any additional information.
title: Pass PMP® - Project Management Professional Exam in 45 Days
